About Devin Simmons
Devin Simmons is a 2LT in TXARNG. Serves as Platoon leader in Charlie Battery, 1st Brigade, 133rd FA regiment.
Received Bachelors of Arts in History and Military Science from The University of Arizona in 2025
Started pursuing Masters in GIS from UTD Fall 2025.

Running Code
When you click the Render button a document will be generated that includes both content and the output of embedded code. You can embed code like this:

1 + 1

[1] 4
